    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR5c0124-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:19:57.413+09:00">列子说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:20:15.48+09:00">＂领会真意的人</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:20:56.26+09:00">什么都知道的人也无须言说。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:21:11.444+09:00">将无言当作表述，也算是一种言说；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:21:24.909+09:00">将无知当作知道，也算是一种有知。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:21:42.54+09:00">而以无言作为不加表述，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:25:33.723+09:00">以无知作为不知道，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:25:50.644+09:00">也是一种言说和有知。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:26:05.589+09:00">所以也没有什么不能说的，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:26:16.195+09:00">也就没有什么不知道的；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:26:52.077+09:00">不过如此而已。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:26:26.4+09:00">也没有什么值得说的，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:26:47.41+09:00">也就没有什么要知道的。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-6a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:37:34.46+09:00">你们为什么还要无端惊惧呢？”</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
